624  static int CompareHeaders(const void *pArg1, const void *pArg2)
625  {
626  CZipFileHeader* pHeader1 = *(CZipFileHeader**)pArg1;
627  CZipFileHeader* pHeader2 = *(CZipFileHeader**)pArg2;
628 
629  if (pHeader1 == pHeader2)
630  return 0;
631 
632  if (pHeader1->m_uVolumeStart == pHeader2->m_uVolumeStart)
633  {
634  if (pHeader1->m_uOffset < pHeader2->m_uOffset)
635  return -1;
636  else if (pHeader1->m_uOffset > pHeader2->m_uOffset)
637  return 1;
638  // if we have two headers with the same offset on the same volume,
639  // we want them to be next to each other so that we can throw an exception while verifying headers after sorting
640  else
641  return 0;
642  }
643  else if (pHeader1->m_uVolumeStart < pHeader2->m_uVolumeStart)
644  return -1;
645  else // if (pHeader1->m_uVolumeStart > pHeader2->m_uVolumeStart)
646  return 1;
647  }

653  static int CompareFindFastCollate(const void* pArg1, const void* pArg2)
654  {
655  CZipFindFast* pHeader1 = *(CZipFindFast**)pArg1;
656  CZipFindFast* pHeader2 = *(CZipFindFast**)pArg2;
657  return pHeader1->m_pHeader->GetFileName().Collate(pHeader2->m_pHeader->GetFileName());
658  }
659 
660  static int CompareFindFastCollateNoCase(const void* pArg1, const void* pArg2)
661  {
662  CZipFindFast* pHeader1 = *(CZipFindFast**)pArg1;
663  CZipFindFast* pHeader2 = *(CZipFindFast**)pArg2;
664  return pHeader1->m_pHeader->GetFileName().CollateNoCase(pHeader2->m_pHeader->GetFileName());
665  }
